  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increase in thefts of spare parts from motorcycles parked in petrol queues in Yali",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Incidents of theft of spare parts from motorbikes queuing up to get fuel are on the rise in Jharkhand.",
        "The front part of a motorcycle that was left in a queue yesterday Friday night to get fuel near a petrol filling station in Kodikamam area of \u200b\u200bJaffna has been damaged.",
        "Meanwhile, a side part of the \"Japan 200\" motorcycle, which was queued to get fuel near the Achuveli filling station a few days ago, was damaged. The owner said that its value is more than 12 thousand.",
        "In this way, the incidents of side mirrors, signals, horns and other parts of motorcycles left in the queues at night are increasing."
      ],
